{
  "stem": "19596.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they floated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They dangled.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "No-- no-- no-- no hood.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the most courageous people I have ever seen hung was the Serbs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They spit in the Germans' faces and said, we'll get you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You won't survive that war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We'll get you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They stood up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, I heard from other people-- I don't care what they say here now about the Serbs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I got great respect for the Serbs, because the Serbs were the only one who were interfering with the transports.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They stopped two or three transports.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They killed all the Germans on top of the guards and they opened the doors and they took the Jews with them in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From people who had been taken in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- in displaced persons camps in Germany [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] after the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look, anybody who was in Auschwitz and he-- he had plenty-- he saw further than just his barrack would witness brutalities all the time, particular by-- by-- by Germans, by German kapos, by oberkapos, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] by Polnish-- half-Polnish and half-Germans, which are from Schleswig, you know, Poznania.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kick them, mistreat them, beat them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they were sadists and the-- and those people were helpless and weak.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they wanted to make a good eye in the Germans' eyes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They want to show themself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Germans had to stop prisoner kapos to-- there was more people killed by prisoners than there were by Germans.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Inmates.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Croatians, Germans, Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, in Auschwitz, we hardly had any seniority in Jewish-- all the Jewish kapos and things like that was all happening in Birkenau [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] or in the Gypsy camps.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
